About 20-25 grams of high-quality protein after exercise, every 4 hours has been shown to maximize the anabolic response in muscle.
Even when consuming enough protein after exercise, adding alcohol reduced muscle growth by 24%, only partially 'rescuing' the protein's effect.
Phishers continue to alter the source code of the web pages used in their attacks to mimic changes to legitimate websites of spoofed organizations and to avoid detection by phishing countermeasures. Manipulations can be as subtle as source code changes or as apparent as adding or removing significant content. To appropriately respond to these changes to phishing campaigns, a set of algorithms is used to identify phishing websites based on their content, using a large database of known phishing attacks targeting various brands. Some experiments have shown that certain content-based approaches can detect phishing websites with a high success rate and few false positives.
It has been hypothesized that eating small, frequent meals enhances fat loss and helps to achieve better weight maintenance. Several observational studies lend support to this hypothesis, with an inverse relationship noted between the frequency of eating and adiposity. The purpose of this narrative review is to present and discuss a meta-analysis with regression that evaluated experimental research on meal frequency with respect to changes in fat mass and lean mass. However, a single study's results may have skewed the findings, so it's unclear if eating more frequently really helps with weight loss. Feeding frequency was positively associated with reductions in fat mass and body fat percentage as well as an increase in fat-free mass. However, sensitivity analysis of the data showed that the positive findings were the product of a single study, casting doubt as to whether more frequent meals confer beneficial effects on body composition. In conclusion, although the initial results of this meta-analysis suggest a potential benefit of increased feeding frequencies for enhancing body composition, these findings need to be interpreted with circumspection.
